The Leader Of INRI Evangelical Spiritual Church, Primate Elijah Ayodele, on Monday prophesied a bomb attack in Abuja. Primate Ayodele issued the prophecy while urging the Nigerian Army and Department of State Services (DSS) to protect Nigeria’s borders. The clergyman urged the DSS, Army and other security agents to fortify Nigeria’s borders because he foresees an attack by some external forces. I foresee State of Emergency, delayed 2023 election in Nigeria – Primate Ayodele warns Buhari In a statement forwarded to DAILY POST, the cleric stated that if the attack of the external forces is successful, it will affect the security of Nigeria more. He urged the Nigerian government to provide the necessary weapons and equipment needed to fortify the security at the borders. According to Primate Ayodele: ‘’Nigerian government must work on the security of their borders because I foresee external forces striking over there. The Nigerian Army, DSS, Police should protect the borders at all cost because of these external forces. “I foresee external forces attacking Nigerian borders which will affect security in the country. Abuja should be secured against bombings.’’ I foresee massive protest that’ll shut down Nigeria – Primate Ayodele warns Buhari